  "text": "1. Conjecture 1 : The widely believed conjecture that the polynomial hierarchy (PH) does not collapse to its 3rd level. [CITATION_1] 2. Conjecture 2 : Approximating the output probabilities + O(1) for a constant fraction of unitaries U y ∈ U E is P-hard.",
